### 1. Health check - Server çalışıyor mu?
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### 2. Tüm kullanıcıları listele (henüz boş olmalı)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users

### 3. İLK KULLANICIYI OLUŞTUR! 🎯
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "yusuf@subtrack.dev",
  "password": "supersecret123",
  "name": "Yusuf Koşar"
}

### 4. Tekrar listele (artık 1 kullanıcı var)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users

### 5. Aynı email'le tekrar oluşturmayı dene (409 Conflict bekliyoruz)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "yusuf@subtrack.dev",
  "password": "anothertry",
  "name": "Yusuf 2"
}

### 6. Şifre olmadan dene (400 Bad Request bekliyoruz)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 7. Çok kısa şifre dene (400 Bad Request bekliyoruz)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "short@example.com",
  "password": "123"
}

### 8. İkinci geçerli kullanıcı oluştur
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@subtrack.dev",
  "password": "demopassword123",
  "name": "Demo User"
}

### TEST 9: Email formatı yanlış (Zod yakalamalı)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "password": "validpass123"
}

### TEST 10: Boşluklu/büyük harfli email (Zod normalize etmeli)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "   YUSUF.TEST@EXAMPLE.COM   ",
  "password": "validpass123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### TEST 11: Birden fazla validation hatası (hepsi tek seferde dönmeli)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid",
  "password": "ab"
}

### TEST 12: Çok uzun email (255 karakter limiti)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa@example.com",
  "password": "validpass123"
}

### TEST 13: Olmayan endpoint (404 testi - yeni format)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/nonexistent

### TEST 14: AppError fırlatma testi (duplicate email - 409)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "yusuf@subtrack.dev",
  "password": "newpassword123",
  "name": "Different Name"
}

### TEST 15: GET tek kullanıcı (henüz endpoint yok - 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/some-id

### TEST 16: Sağlık kontrolü (200 - error handler etkilenmemeli)
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### ========================================
### AUTH TESTS
### ========================================

### A1: Yeni kullanıcı kayıt (register)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "yusuf-jwt@subtrack.dev",
  "password": "supersecret123",
  "name": "Auth Test User"
}

### A2: Login (başarılı)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "yusuf-jwt@subtrack.dev",
  "password": "supersecret123"
}

### A3: Login (yanlış şifre - 401 bekliyoruz)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "yusuf-jwt@subtrack.dev",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### A4: Login (olmayan email - aynı 401 hatası bekliyoruz)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nonexistent@subtrack.dev",
  "password": "anything"
}

### A5: Protected endpoint - token YOK (401 bekliyoruz)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users

### A6: Protected endpoint - YANLIŞ token (401 bekliyoruz)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer fake.invalid.token

### A7: Get current user - token YOK (401 bekliyoruz)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me

