### ========================================
### SUBSCRIPTION TESTS
### ========================================
### Önce A2 (Login) çalıştır, "token" alanını kopyala.
### Aşağıdaki @authToken değişkenine yapıştır.

@authToken = BURAYA_TOKEN_YAPISTIR

### S1: Login (token al)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "yusuf-jwt@subtrack.dev",
  "password": "supersecret123"
}

### S2: Aboneliklerimi listele (boş olmalı)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### S3: Yeni Netflix aboneliği oluştur
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Netflix",
  "price": 99.99,
  "currency": "TRY",
  "billingCycle": "MONTHLY",
  "category": "Entertainment",
  "startDate": "2026-01-01",
  "nextPaymentDate": "2026-06-01",
  "notes": "Premium plan, 4K"
}

### S4: Spotify aboneliği oluştur
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Spotify",
  "price": 59.99,
  "currency": "TRY",
  "billingCycle": "MONTHLY",
  "category": "Music",
  "startDate": "2026-02-15",
  "nextPaymentDate": "2026-05-20"
}

### S5: Tüm aboneliklerimi listele (artık 2 tane var)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### S6: Yaklaşan ödemeler (varsayılan 7 gün)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### S7: Yaklaşan ödemeler (30 gün)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/upcoming?days=30
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### S8: Tek bir abonelik detayı (önce S3'ün cevabından id'yi kopyala)
### S3'ün response'undan subscription.id alanını @subId değişkenine yapıştır
@subId = BURAYA_ABONELIK_ID_YAPISTIR

GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/{{subId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### S9: Aboneliği güncelle (fiyat artışı)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/{{subId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "price": 119.99,
  "notes": "Premium plan, 4K - Fiyat zammı sonrası"
}

### S10: Aboneliği pasifleştir (iptal etmeden)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/{{subId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "isActive": false
}

### ========================================
### HATA / GÜVENLİK TESTLERİ
### ========================================

### S11: Token olmadan dene (401 bekliyoruz)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions

### S12: Geçersiz fiyat (negatif, 400 bekliyoruz)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Invalid Sub",
  "price": -50,
  "startDate": "2026-01-01",
  "nextPaymentDate": "2026-06-01"
}

### S13: Geçmiş tarih ile next payment (400 bekliyoruz)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Time Travel",
  "price": 10,
  "startDate": "2020-01-01",
  "nextPaymentDate": "2020-06-01"
}

### S14: Geçersiz UUID (400 bekliyoruz)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/not-a-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### S15: Var olmayan ID (404 bekliyoruz)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### S16: Trial olarak işaretle ama trialEndsAt verme (400 bekliyoruz)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Disney+ Free Trial",
  "price": 0,
  "startDate": "2026-05-01",
  "nextPaymentDate": "2026-06-01",
  "isTrial": true
}

### S17: Aboneliği sil
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/{{subId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### S18: Silinen aboneliği tekrar GET (404 bekliyoruz)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/subscriptions/{{subId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
